---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import CtaBand from '../../components/CtaBand.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Scam Protection Add-On for Home-Care Agencies | Spry"
  description="Offer client families measurable scam-resilience training — deeper trust and a new revenue line for your agency."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap prose">
      <p class="kicker">For home care</p>
      <h1>The safety add-on your client families will thank you for.</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        You're already the trusted safety layer in your clients' lives. Spry extends that
        trust to the fastest-growing threat they face — and adds a recurring revenue line while it
        does.
      </p>
      <p>
        Home-care clients are precisely the population scammers target: older, living
        independently, managing their own phones and inboxes. Their adult children hired you
        because they can't be there every day. Spry gives your agency a concrete answer for
        the threat that arrives through the phone line — with zero clinical burden on caregivers.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--paper">
    <div class="wrap prose">
      <h2>How it works for agencies</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Resell or bundle Spry to client families — revenue share or margin on per-client pricing</li>
        <li>Enrollment folds into your existing intake and consent process</li>
        <li>Families get the Resilience Report with your agency's name alongside ours</li>
        <li>
          Caregivers get a simple heads-up when a client misses a drill, turning coaching into a
          warm human moment (“Mrs. Alvarez, did you see that practice text? Let's look together”)
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Why agencies win</h2>
      <p>
        Differentiation in a crowded referral market; stickier client relationships (a monthly
        report is a monthly reminder of your value); and a genuinely protective service — the
        average reported loss for a senior fraud victim is around $39,000, which for many families
        is the home-care budget itself.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaBand
    headline="Founding-agency pilots are open."
    body="A 20-minute call covers pilot terms, revenue share, and how enrollment fits your intake."
    cta="Book a 20-minute call"
    href="mailto:hello@sawtoothtechnologies.com?subject=Spry%20home-care%20pilot"
  />
</Base>

<style>
  ul { padding-left: 1.2em; }
  ul li { margin-bottom: 0.6em; }
</style>
